Given a BST, modify it so that all greater values in the given BST are added to every node.this was asked without using a static or global member

yha pr we do reverse inorder traversal RNL

modify(Node root,int sum)
{

if(root==null)return null;

 mdify(root.right,sum);
 sum+=root.data;
 root.data=sum;
 
 modify(root.left,sum);

 





}
